## Source-of-truth is the Korean `msgid` (legal-tech draft register, per
## DESIGN.md §4 v31). The `msgstr` mirrors the `msgid` for the ko locale
## because the source uses Hangul directly; the en locale falls back to
## the msgid.
##
## #. TODO native-speaker review:
